Cache-Control: no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate, post-check=0, pre-check=0.
Connection: close.
Last-Modified: Thu, 27 Jan 2011 12:33:34 GMT.
Content-Length: 885.
Vary: Accept-Encoding.
Content-Type: text/xml.

